<div class="session-explorer-root">
  <h1>What Was Actually Happening</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">10-day Claude Code session · 426 messages · 13.1M tokens</p>
  <p class="subtitle">My own categorization of one real session after the fact — not a universal benchmark, but a useful pattern.</p>

  <p class="section-label">Session at a glance</p>
  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="num">426</div>
